videos.description: Baylor's Jo Lual-Acil Jr. drives to the rim, gets forced outside and extends with the underhand for the basket.
videos.headline: Lual-Acuil Jr. extends for the underhand layup

videos.description: Ethan Happ bounces to Khalil Iverson between defenders and rocks the rim with two hands for the Badgers.
videos.headline: Happ sets up Iverson for big dunk

videos.description: Baylor's Tristan Clark sprints out in transition and jams it home with one hand.
videos.headline: Clark throws down one-hander on fast break

videos.description: Nuni Omot gets the tough finish to go on a behind the back pass from Manu Lecomte for Baylor.
videos.headline: Lecomte goes around the back to Omot

videos.description: Manu Lecomte sets up Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. with the big alley-oop and-1 for the Bears.
videos.headline: Lual-Acuil Jr. rolls off the pick for the alley-oop and-1

videos.description: Brad Davidson muscles off his defender and knocks down a big stepback 3-pointer for the Badgers.
videos.headline: Davidson creates space for stepback 3

videos.description: Ethan Happ is in the right spot on the missed 3-pointer, as he gets the board and the putback lay-in to cut Baylor's lead to four.
videos.headline: Happ gets the putback for Badgers
